The,AbleSMS,API,allows,users,to,automate,the,sending,and,receiving,of,SMS,messages,by,integrating,AbleSMS,services,directly,with,the,user,s,business,applications,websites,or,in,house,software,The,SOAP,API,can,be,used,to,delete,messages,in,a,SMS,inbox,send,and,retrieve,messages,and,generate,reports,on,inbox,and,messaging,activity